reviewText: I have watched the first 3 and they are very good. I have previously seen the 5th movie and i know it is good. I only gave it a  rating of 3 because the sound quality is poor.
I ordered the wrong movie. I'm wanted an earlier movie that was called "The Day the World Ended." but the video quality of the movies that were on this DVD was acceptable.
I bought this for Anaconda.  Let's face it, the movie sucks and John Voight's portrayal of a South American was embarassing, but the moving is a guilty pleasure of mine, and I like watching it.
thank you very much i like it very much and it came on time, thank you again.
